float usage guide:
    1. website: css.maxdesign.com.au/floatutorial
    2. Floats and "clear": Elements following a floated element will wrap around the floated element. If you do
       not want this to occur, you can apply the "clear" property to these following elements.(which means 
       isolated instead of wrap around)





